title: UK advises Trump not to dump the Iran deal
text:
UK advises Trump not to dump the Iran deal 10:00pm IST - 01:20
British Foreign Secretary Boris Johnson has appealed to U.S. President Donald Trump not to pull out of the Iran nuclear agreement, saying the deal had weaknesses but they could be addressed given time. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
